un der khor hot zikh gezamlt tsunoyf un er iz gevorn bay a hundert mentshn.

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:48.313
un mir tretn oyf Varshe in Splendye teater, tsvey toyznt nayn hundert mentshn. mir gibn a kontsert.

00:15:51.053 --> 00:15:57.425
a yugntlekher hot aza gvaldikn viln tsu shteyn oyf der bret in a teater.

00:16:00.840 --> 00:16:11.044
fun di fun dem khor hot zikh oysgesheylt fuftsn BOYS, besoykhem mit mir,

00:16:12.113 --> 00:16:17.456
ikh bin geven a groyser shtifer, un fuftsn meydlekh.

00:16:18.154 --> 00:16:22.148
un dos iz geven alts porlekh hobn arumgegangen, nisht keyn farheyrate.

00:16:24.229 --> 00:16:27.851
un m'hot gemakht a dram-krayz, tsu shpiln teater.

00:16:32.903 --> 00:16:38.671
mir firn oyf di ershte forshtelung in grestn yidishn teater.

00:16:38.671 --> 00:16:43.106
Kaminske's teater hot ir gehert, Roboshne eyns. Kaminske's teater.

00:16:43.500 --> 00:16:47.493
nisht bay nakht, vayl m'hot nisht gekent krign dos teater bay nakht, nor mitog.

00:16:48.613 --> 00:16:58.800
firn men dortn oyf, vayl m'iz gevezn ale a bisl geneygt TO link.

00:17:00.493 --> 00:17:11.793
mir hobn men gedorfn oyffirn a pyese fun Gorki's, efsher hot ir geleyent Maksim Gorki.

00:17:11.935 --> 00:17:19.590
zay- er bashraybt vegn a muter. mir dort dort iz mit revolutsyonerishe inhalt.

00:17:20.625 --> 00:17:25.187
nu az m'hot gevolt legalizirn, hot men nisht getort,

00:17:25.187 --> 00:17:29.984
hot men legalizirt, Sholem Ash hot geshribn vegn di m- a mamen.

00:17:30.193 --> 00:17:34.473
hot men legalizirt Sholem Ash, un geshpilt hot men Gorki's.

00:17:36.066 --> 00:17:41.764
nisht vikhtik, un do iz es dervayle gevezn fun di provints zenen gekumen, m'hot undz geRENT.

00:17:44.014 --> 00:17:51.281
gevorn artistn. ANYWAY, un derfun hobn mir keyn parnose nisht getsoygn.

00:17:51.608 --> 00:17:54.858
s'alts gelt alts iz gegangen far di parteyen.

00:17:56.940 --> 00:18:07.009
in ende di dray un draysikstn yor bashlis ikh tsu geyn far zikh. genug gearbet bay yenem.

00:18:08.517 --> 00:18:11.616
ober ikh hob nisht gekent zogn az ikh gey far zikh.

00:18:12.651 --> 00:18:18.956
zog ikh zey di balbat- mayn balboste mitn balbos, zey hobn mir azoy gut bahandlt, ikh for keyn Pariz.

00:18:19.452 --> 00:18:23.108
er veyst, ir veyst dokh az mentsh- m'fort keyn Pariz, UNK.

00:18:24.143 --> 00:18:26.030
meyle zogt er, "vos ken ikh tun?

00:18:26.030 --> 00:18:31.443
ven du geyst ergets arbetn, iz gelt iz nisht keyn, gebn mer. iz nokh a por dolar.

00:18:31.922 --> 00:18:36.016
BUT az du geyt forn keyn Pariz, ken ikh shoyn gornisht tun."

00:18:36.934 --> 00:18:40.438
ikh dervayl hob mir gehat geRENT a tsimer vu ikh zol kenen arbetn.

00:18:40.798 --> 00:18:45.399
ayngeordnt a shayer a ⟨shayberke⟩ aza, a kleyne far zikh.

00:18:47.481 --> 00:18:50.074
ikh zits azoy un arbet, kumt arayn di balboste.

00:18:50.839 --> 00:18:55.878
zog zi, "panye Yizak, ir fort nisht keyn Pariz.

00:18:58.467 --> 00:19:04.856
ir zogt nisht emes. BUT ikh derken," zogt zi, "in ayere oygn az ir fort nisht keyn Pariz." geven zeyer a kluge froy.

00:19:05.402 --> 00:19:08.214
ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent gornisht zogn, zog ikh, "hert oys.

00:19:08.271 --> 00:19:12.011
ikh for nisht keyn Pariz. ikh hob nisht gezogt emes.

00:19:13.114 --> 00:19:19.081
ikh gey arum mit a meydl, ikh trakht vegn khasene hobn, ikh gey far zikh."

00:19:20.117 --> 00:19:25.224
zogt der balbos, ikh muz mitforn vu d- vu host geRENT un vu du geyst arbetn."

00:19:26.648 --> 00:19:34.421
ANYWAY, mayn CLIENTAL iz geven a bagrenetste: mayne khaveyrim

00:19:34.697 --> 00:19:38.049
nu mayne khaveyrim zenen gevezn azoy raykh azoy vi ikh.

00:19:38.612 --> 00:19:41.891
un az eyner hot zikh gemakht a SUIT, hot er getrogn finef zeks yor.

00:19:41.891 --> 00:19:44.023
nakher hot er gedarft makhn oyf der linker zayt.

00:19:45.970 --> 00:19:51.805
ANYWAY, ikh hob ongehoybn epes gekrign arbet etlekhene,

00:19:51.805 --> 00:19:56.544
eyner hot men arayn⟨UNK⟩ an andern CUSTOMER. ober s'nisht geven tsu fil.

00:19:57.883 --> 00:20:07.293
opgearbet, un s'gekumen in fir un draysikstn yor, in JUIN dem fift- in zibetn,

00:20:08.481 --> 00:20:13.503
iz azoy. ven ikh hob gearbet, ikh hob shoyn fardint, afilesh ikh hob gearbet bay yenem,

00:20:13.864 --> 00:20:19.528
iz dos meydl vos ikh bin mit arumgegangen, hob ikh gedorfn koyfn a DRESS.

00:20:20.192 --> 00:20:22.903
dos iz geven ayer tsukunftike kale?

00:20:21.296 --> 00:20:25.314
an oreme meydl a, an orem meydl a, nokh erger vi ikh.

00:20:25.575 --> 00:20:29.096
dos iz geven ayer tsukunfte,

00:20:26.611 --> 00:20:29.130
mayn mayn shvoger's a shvegerin.

00:20:31.768 --> 00:20:37.702
ikh ho- ikh hob ir gedorfn gebn tsu esn. zi hot gevoynt bay der shvester,

00:20:39.497 --> 00:20:43.620
vayl zey hobn gehat dortn a voynung, eyn tsimer dortn, hobn hobn ge⟨UNK⟩,

00:20:43.620 --> 00:20:48.446
iz der foter irer geshtorbn, hot men epes a halb gegebn ir, a halb di andere shvester.

00:20:48.446 --> 00:20:51.354
vayl der shvoger hot oysgenart bay ir, a gantse mayse.

00:20:50.955 --> 00:20:51.539
yo.

00:20:51.360 --> 00:20:52.974
s'dokh nisht vikhtik di aleser.

00:20:54.415 --> 00:21:02.508
iz der khevreman un di khaveyrim, "du darfst ir say vi say gebn esn, du darfst ir say vi say ontun, hob khasene!"

00:21:03.983 --> 00:21:11.587
iz in fuftstn JUNE, ze'mir aroyfgegangen tsu a rov, mir ho'mir khasene gehat.

00:21:12.589 --> 00:21:16.886
geven mayne mayn bruder iz gevezn, der tsveyter iz gekumen, mayn muter,

00:21:16.943 --> 00:21:19.218
di mame iz gekumen?

00:21:17.833 --> 00:21:20.126
UNK zenen gekumen tsu der khasene.

00:21:20.487 --> 00:21:27.400
s'geven a khasene s'ge-, s'geven a khasene un broyt mit vursht, un fertik.

00:21:27.928 --> 00:21:33.351
un mayne khaveyrim hobn nisht gevust. keynem nisht.

00:21:33.359 --> 00:21:34.987
vi azoy hot zi geheysn?

00:21:35.079 --> 00:21:35.851
vos?

00:21:35.740 --> 00:21:37.743
di kale, vi azoy hot zi geheysn?

00:21:37.814 --> 00:21:41.085
Hinde. Hinde Royznboym.

00:21:43.437 --> 00:21:45.928
zi iz yetst geshtorbn akht monatn tsurik.

00:21:46.322 --> 00:21:48.746
ikh hob gevoynt mit ir tsvey un zekhtsik yor.

00:21:52.009 --> 00:21:57.571
ANYWAY, tsu morgns nokh der khasene, arbetn.

00:22:00.075 --> 00:22:07.460
un zi hot gekrign a JOB in a groyse FACTORY vos m'hot gemakht

00:22:08.395 --> 00:22:14.986
kurts ge- ge- ge- geSMOKED geSMOKED fleysh, konzervn, vos s'gegangen oyf oysland.

00:22:16.258 --> 00:22:21.078
un zi iz dortn gevezn epes a por teg un m'hot ir gemakht far a forman.

00:22:21.439 --> 00:22:26.512
hot zi gehat zeks hundert mentshn unter ir hant. s'gegangen dray SHIFTS.

00:22:26.974 --> 00:22:30.326
s'iz aroysgekumen a mol tsu zayn bay nakht a gantse nakht dort.

00:22:31.176 --> 00:22:35.254
ANYWAY, fun di ale iz nisht geven keyn tsu groyse parnose.

00:22:36.947 --> 00:22:48.146
s'gekumen zumer iz nokh der khasene, nu tsi s'ge- iz geven dem zelbn zumer, tsi dem nekstn zumer?

00:22:48.220 --> 00:22:52.972
