00:23:42.422 --> 00:23:46.668
un zi hot geshribn tsu zey, az zi geyt khasene hobn,

00:23:47.164 --> 00:23:52.339
un zenen orem, zi hot nisht keyn gelt mer. hot zenen geshikt far hundert dolar.

00:23:53.307 --> 00:23:58.262
