zey hobn nokh nisht gehat keyn kinder, yunge mentshn, freylekhe mentshn.

00:25:43.129 --> 00:25:48.742
ikh hob mit zey bald dem ershtn tog azoy noent bakent, m'hot gezungen tsuzamen,

00:25:48.883 --> 00:25:53.180
m'iz geshlofn in a tsimer, hot es gemuzt zayn a CONVENTION HALL.

00:25:53.592 --> 00:25:57.129
iz geshtanen oyfgeshtelt betlekh, bin ikh geshlofn ale in in eyn ROOM.

