00:26:19.309 --> 00:26:25.496
zogt er, "ikh bin a tsushnayder. un ikh arbet in a gesheft oyfn Marshelkoske

00:26:26.532 --> 00:26:30.053
in a groyser fabrik. di fabrik heyst Tseder.

