mir kumen krik tsu forn, forndik aheym zenen ale in di TRAIN, un mikh hot men nisht arayngelozt.

00:26:57.784 --> 00:27:01.001
s'geshtanen a zelner un a tsivilner, er hot mikh nisht arayngelozt.

