"du arbetst far zikh? tsu vemen firstu dos?" zog ikh, "tsu Tseder."

00:28:20.185 --> 00:28:27.181
"du first, du arbetst in Tseder? kenst dokh makhn mayne oykhet. kum ze mikh bay nakht." do un do.

